<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>We are getting in touch today as we believe that there is </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">an outstanding balance of £0.00 owed for policy {!Policy__c.Id}</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>We would love to discuss this with you with a view to getting this resolved. Could you please call us on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, or alternatively, let us know a convenient time for us to call you.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
